{"id":146612,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/转载我准备好了/","date":"2011-04-22T19:05:23Z","modified":"2011-04-22T19:05:23Z","title":"[转载]我准备好了","content":"<div>\n<div><span><strong>原文地址：</strong><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_7bbb3f0f0100q704.html\" title=\"我准备好了\">我准备好了</a></span><span><strong>作者：</strong><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/2075868943\" title=\"MZ54321\">MZ54321</a></span></div>\n<div>\n<p><strong> <wbr><br />\n不要再来找我，我不会合作，如果非要来，就带上你们的刑具吧。</strong></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr> <wbr>  <wbr> <a href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s7.sinaimg.cn/orignal/7bbb3f0fta0912bb409c6\"><img height=\"640\" src=\"http://s7.sinaimg.cn/middle/7bbb3f0fta0912bb409c6&#038;690\" width=\"480\" /></a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>我准备好了。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>或者说，我没有什么可以准备的。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>一个人，这就是我的全部，是别人可能获得、我可以奉献的全部。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>在需要的时候我不会犹豫，不会含糊的。<br />\n　　<br />\n如果有什么可以留恋，</strong></p>\n<p><strong>那就是生命带来的奇迹，</strong></p>\n<p><strong>这个奇迹就是我们每一个人都是一样的，</strong></p>\n<p><strong>人人平等的游戏，</strong></p>\n<p><strong>还有随之而来的幻想和自由。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>来自任何权利、任何方式的威胁，我都视作是对人的尊严、理性的威胁，是对生的可能性的威胁。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>我要学会面对。放心，我学得很快，不会让你们失望的。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>在不久前失去生的权利的那些孩子，他们的群体死亡，帮助我理解了个体生命和社会的含义。</p>\n<p>　　<br />\n拒绝犬儒，拒绝合作，拒绝恐吓，拒绝喝茶，在这些问题上是没有可以商量的。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>还是那句话，</strong></p>\n<p><strong>不要再来找我，我不会合作，如果非要来，就带上你们的刑具吧。</strong></p>\n<p>\n<span><br />\n【</span><span>按：起初，我们最好的作家在囚室里。然后，我们最有良知的律师在囚室里。现在，我们最好的艺术家也在囚室里。似乎不被关进号子，就不足以体现他们的优秀。下一个被用这种方式加以表彰的会是谁呢？</span><span>】</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n离开了谎言，这个世界将空荡荡。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n你如果希望了解你的祖国，你已经走上了犯罪的道路。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n每个人都要说出真话来，如果都这样，他们就完了。不要觉得没有用。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n在人的所有的室外运动中，有什么比向傻逼暴君扔石头更优美的动作呢？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n我每秒钟都受到威胁，因为我生活在一个非常有危险性的国度里。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n我怕的要命，不是无所畏惧，或许比其他人更要害怕。我之所以勇敢，是因为我知道危险就在那里，如果我不采取行动，危险会越来越强大。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7.<span> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr> <wbr><wbr><wbr></span></span></span><br />\n<span><br />\n他们最怕的就是你不怕他！</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=752465\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe me!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":966,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}